Name: UfoScare
About the game: UFOScare is a roguelike with RPG elements. You are a space ranger who participates in an operation to free Mars. No one expected that our base would be attacked by such a huge number of aliens that appeared from nowhere. Your task is to reflect as many waves as possible and stay alive, but is it possible? Peculiarities: - Nice graphics. - Random level generation. - Several types of weapons. - Leveling the character.
